(19227,3,0,"Hey! Hey, $r! I be havin\' just the thing for ya. Ya ever see a tikbalang? Frightenin\' creatures. Prone to stealin\' ya away. What ya need is one of my tikbalang wards. Guaranteed to ward away all tikbalangs!",12,0,100,0,0,0,16318,"Griftah");
