(19227,4,0,"Look over here, $c! I got somethin\' for ya. Just what ya need. It\'s soap, right... and it\'s on a rope! No offense, $G man:honey;, but yer a little ripe, know what I\'m sayin\'?",12,0,100,0,0,0,16319,"Griftah");
